data.description: Discover the charm of 29130 Sunswept Drive in the scenic Lake Elsinore area. This inviting property combines the tranquility of suburban living with the convenience of modern amenities. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious, open-concept living area bathed in natural light. The heart of the home is a well-appointed kitchen, and ample storage, perfect for both casual family meals and sophisticated entertaining. The home offers a series of cozy bedrooms, including a luxurious master suite with an en-suite bathroom, ensuring a private and peaceful retreat for relaxation. Outside, the landscaped backyard is an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings or quiet evenings under the stars. Situated in a desirable Lake Elsinore neighborhood, this home is moments away from shopping, dining, and leisure activities, offering the perfect balance of serenity and accessibility.
